title: scatter_plot
content:
def get_scatter(X, y, title, svd=True):
    """
    Функция для визуализации данных на плоскости с использованием метода SVD.

    Параметры:
    X - матрица признаков размерности (n_samples, n_features), где n_samples - количество объектов, а n_features - количество признаков.
    y - вектор меток классов размерности (n_samples).
    title - заголовок графика.
    svd - флаг, указывающий, нужно ли использовать метод SVD для снижения размерности данных (по умолчанию True).

    Возвращаемое значение:
    График с точками на плоскости, где каждая точка представляет объект из набора данных, 
    цвет точки соответствует метке класса, а размер точки зависит от значения вектора y 
    (если значение метки класса равно 1, то размер точки равен 2, в противном случае равен 1).
    """
    if svd:
        # Снижение размерности данных до 2 компонент с помощью метода SVD
        svd = TruncatedSVD(n_components=2)
        X = svd.fit_transform(X)

    # Задание размеров точек на графике в зависимости от метки класса
    sizes = [2 if label == 1 else 1 for label in y]

    # Создание объектов фигуры и осей графика с заданным размером
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15, 8))
    # Рисование точек на графике
    scatter = ax.scatter(X[:, 0], X[:, 1], c=y, cmap=plt.cm.get_cmap('RdYlBu_r'), s=sizes)
    # Задание заголовка графика, а также скрытие делений на осях
    ax.set_title(title)
    ax.set_xticks([])
    ax.set_yticks([])

    # Создание списка объектов типа Line2D, представляющих элементы легенды на графике
    legend_elements = [
        plt.Line2D([0], [0], marker='o', color='w', markersize=8,
                   markerfacecolor=scatter.get_cmap()(1.0), label='Токсичные комментарии'),
        plt.Line2D([0], [0], marker='o', color='w', markersize=8,
                   markerfacecolor=scatter.get_cmap()(0.0), label='Нормальные комментарии')
    ]
    # Добавление легенды на график
    ax.legend(handles=legend_elements)
    # Отображение графика
    plt.show()

    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:layout_height="fill_parent"
    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
    xmlns:card_view="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:orientation="vertical">

    <LinearLayout
        android:layout_width="231dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_gravity="center_vertical"
        android:layout_weight="1"
        android:orientation="vertical"
        android:padding="5dp">

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="260dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:fontFamily="@font/poppinsbold"
            android:text="APP POS TOKO LOREN"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textSize="18sp"
            android:textStyle="bold" />

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="260dp"
            android:layout_height="59dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="0dp"
            android:fontFamily="@font/poppinsregular"
            android:text="APLIKASI POS TOKO LOREN"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textSize="20sp"
            android:textStyle="bold" />
    </LinearLayout>

    <RelativeLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="?attr/actionBarSize"
        android:paddingBottom="10dp"
        android:elevation="999dp"
        android:background="@drawable/gradient_bg_hover"
        android:gravity="bottom"
        android:paddingLeft="10dp"
        android:paddingRight="10dp">

        <ImageView
            android:id="@+id/profile_image"
            android:layout_width="46dp"
            android:layout_height="46dp"
            android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
            android:background="@drawable/main_menu_icon" />

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/txtMarquee"
            android:layout_width="346dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
            android:layout_marginStart="6dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="6dp"
            android:layout_marginBottom="10dp"
            android:layout_toEndOf="@id/profile_image"
            android:layout_toRightOf="@id/profile_image"
            android:ellipsize="marquee"
            android:fontFamily="sans-serif"
            android:gravity="left"
            android:marqueeRepeatLimit="marquee_forever"
            android:singleLine="true"
            android:text="Aplikasi POS Toko Loren"
            android:textColor="#fff"
            android:textSize="15dp" />
    </RelativeLayout>

        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent"
        android:paddingTop="10dp">

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="fill_parent"
            android:layout_height="fill_parent"
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:weightSum="2"
            android:padding="5dp">

                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="match_parent"
                android:orientation="vertical"
                android:weightSum="10"
                android:gravity="center"
                android:padding="10dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="380dp"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center_vertical"
                    android:layout_weight="1"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="5dp">

                        android:textStyle="bold" />

                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="20dp"
                        android:layout_marginTop="10dp"

                    android:layout_width="match_parent"

                </LinearLayout>

                <LinearLayout

                    android:gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="horizontal"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">

                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                        android:foreground="?android:attr/selectableItemBackground"
                        android:clickable="true"
                        android:id="@+id/btnPenjualan"
                        android:layout_width="160dp"
                        android:layout_height="160dp"
                        android:layout_margin="10dp"
                        app:cardElevation="20dp"

                        <LinearLayout

                            android:layout_height="match_parent"

                            android:gravity="center">

                                android:layout_width="64dp"
                                android:layout_height="59dp"
                                android:padding="10dp"

                        </LinearLayout>
                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>

                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                        android:foreground="?android:attr/selectableItemBackground"
                        android:clickable="true"
                        android:layout_width="160dp"
                        android:id="@+id/btnPembelian"
                        android:layout_height="160dp"
                        android:layout_margin="10dp"
                        app:cardElevation="15dp"

                        <LinearLayout

                            android:layout_height="match_parent"
                            android:gravity="center"

                </LinearLayout>

                    android:orientation="horizontal"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">

                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView

                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>

                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
                </LinearLayout>

                <LinearLayout
                    android:clipToPadding="false"
                    android:gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="horizontal"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">

                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                        android:foreground="?android:attr/selectableItemBackground"

                        android:id="@+id/btnLaporan"
                        android:layout_width="160dp"
                        android:layout_height="160dp"
                        android:layout_margin="10dp"
                        app:cardElevation="20dp"
                        app:cardCornerRadius="20dp">

                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="match_parent"
                            android:orientation="vertical"

                                android:layout_height="64dp"
                                android:src="@drawable/ic_laporan"

                            <TextView

                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                                android:textStyle="bold"

                                android:text="Laporan"/>

                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>

                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                        android:foreground="?android:attr/selectableItemBackground"
                        android:clickable="true"
                        android:layout_width="160dp"
                        android:layout_height="160dp"
                        android:layout_margin="10dp"
                        app:cardElevation="15dp"
                        app:cardCornerRadius="15dp">
                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
                </LinearLayout>

            </LinearLayout>

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                android:gravity="center"
                android:textColor="@color/base"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:textSize="13dp"/>
        </LinearLayout>
    </androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>
</LinearLayout>

title: mcMidiJukebox
content:
speaker = peripheral.wrap("bottom")


function mysplit (inputstr, sep)
    if sep == nil then
            sep = "%s"
    end
    local t={}
    for str in string.gmatch(inputstr, "([^"..sep.."]+)") do
            table.insert(t, str)
    end
    return t
end




songName = read()
Play = false --holdover from organ setup. could be more optimized for this

--main code
print("Playing song!")
for line in io.lines(songName) do
    local msg = mysplit(line, ', ')
    if msg[2] == 'off' then
        Play = false
    elseif msg[2] == 'on' then
        Play = true
    end

    sleep(tonumber(msg[1]))
    speaker.playNote(msg[4],1,tonumber(msg[3]))
end
print("end of song!")

#!/usr/b#in/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
'''
SQL lenguaje de consultas estructuras
paradigma declarativo

crear una base de datos llamada prueba:
CREATE DATABASE estacionMetereologica;

quiero ver todos los registros de una tabla Clima_DIA
SELECT * FROM Clima_DIA

motor de base de datos: 
MySQL, MariaDB, PostgreSQL, SQLite  --> soft libre
SQL Server, Oracle --> soft propio

DB-API: API estandar de Python

MySQL: mysql-connector-python, PyMySQL, MySQLdb
PostgreSQL psycopg, pg8000
SQLite: sqlite3 (ya viene instalada)
SQL Server: pymssql, pyodbc
Oracle: cx_Oracle
"""
# el mismo ejemplo para MYSQL
# previamente instalar python -m pip install pymysql

"""
import pymysql

# se conecta a la base
conn = pymysql.connect(
	host='localhost',
	user='usuario',
	passwd='password',
	db='mi_base.db')

# para hacer una consulta SDL necesito un cursor
cursor = conn.cursor()

# puedo ejecutar una consulta SQL: crear una tabla
cursor.execute("CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS personas(nombre VARCHAR(45), edad INT)")

# como modifique la base debo "guardar los datos"
conn.commit()

# creo una tupla de datos
datos = (
	("Juan",30),
	("Luis",11),
	("Vicky",25),
)

for nombre, edad in datos:
	cursor.execute("INSERT INTO personas VALUES(%s,%s?)",(nombre,edad))

conn.commit()

# quiero imprimir
cursor.execute("SELECT * FROM personas")
personas = cursor.fetchall()
print(personas)

# cierro la conexion
conn.close()
'''

# SQL Injection
# >> Ingrese un nombre: Alejandro',22); DELETE FROM personas; --
# >> Ingrese la edad: 30
# INSERT INTO personas VALUES('Alejandro',22); DELETE FROM personas; --,30)


import sqlite3

conn = sqlite3.connect("mi_base.sqlite")

cursor = conn.cursor()

nombre = input("Ingrese un nombre: ")
edad = int(input("Ingrese la edad: "))

# condición correcta (resiste SQL Injection)
# cursor.execute("INSERT INTO personas VALUES(?,?)",(nombre,edad))

# condición peligrosa: si están habilitados los warnings resiste, si no, NO
# lanza
# sqlite3.Warning: You can only execute one statement at a time.
# no da error, dice que solo ejecuta una instrucción a la vez
# cursor.execute(f"INSERT INTO personas VALUES('{nombre}',{edad})")

# condicion LETAL: borra la tabla
cursor.executescript(f"INSERT INTO personas VALUES('{nombre}',{edad})")

conn.commit()
conn.close()

content:
local inventoryFile = fs.open("inventory", "r")
local inventoryData = inventoryFile.readAll()
inventoryFile.close()
local inventory = textutils.unserializeJSON(inventoryData)

local searchInput = ""
local quantityInput = 0

local function clearInput()
    searchInput = ""
    quantityInput = 0
end

local function drawGUI()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)

    -- Draw search input
    term.setTextColor(colors.white)
    term.write("Item Search: ")
    term.setTextColor(colors.gray)
    term.write(searchInput)

    -- Filter items based on search input
    local filteredItems = {}
    for itemName, itemData in pairs(inventory) do
        if string.find(itemName:lower(), searchInput:lower()) then
            table.insert(filteredItems, { name = itemName, count = itemData[#itemData].quantity })
        end
    end

    -- Draw matching items
    term.setTextColor(colors.white)
    term.setCursorPos(1, 3)
    if #filteredItems > 0 then
        term.write("Matching Items:")
        for i = 1, math.min(#filteredItems, 10) do
            local item = filteredItems[i]
            term.setCursorPos(1, i + 3)
            term.setTextColor(colors.white)
            term.write(item.name)
            term.setTextColor(colors.gray)
            term.write(" (" .. item.count .. ")")
        end
    else
        term.write("No items found.")
    end

    -- Draw quantity input and buttons
    term.setTextColor(colors.white)
    term.setCursorPos(1, 16)
    term.write("Quantity: ")
    term.setTextColor(colors.gray)
    term.write(tostring(quantityInput))

    -- Draw buttons
    term.setCursorPos(4, 18)
    term.setTextColor(colors.white)
    term.write("-64")
    term.setCursorPos(10, 18)
    term.write("-1")
    term.setCursorPos(15, 18)
    term.write("+1")
    term.setCursorPos(20, 18)
    term.write("+64")
    term.setCursorPos(30, 18)
    term.setTextColor(colors.green)
    term.write("Go")
end

local function updateGUI()
    clearInput()
    drawGUI()
end

updateGUI()

while true do
    local _, x, y = os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")

    if y == 18 then
        if x >= 4 and x <= 7 then
            quantityInput = quantityInput - 64
            if quantityInput < 0 then
                quantityInput = 0
            end
            updateGUI()
        elseif x >= 10 and x <= 12 then
            quantityInput = quantityInput - 1
            if quantityInput < 0 then
                quantityInput = 0
            end
            updateGUI()
        elseif x >= 15 and x <= 16 then
            quantityInput = quantityInput + 1
            updateGUI()
        elseif x >= 20 and x <= 22 then
            quantityInput = quantityInput + 64
            updateGUI()
        elseif x >= 30 and x <= 31 then
            break
        end
    end
end

-- Perform the action to deliver the selected item with the specified quantity
local filteredItems = {}
for itemName, itemData in pairs(inventory) do
    if string.find(itemName:lower(), searchInput:lower()) then
        table.insert(filteredItems, { name = itemName, count = itemData[#itemData].quantity })
    end
end

local selectedItem = filteredItems[1] -- Select the first item by default
local quantity = quantityInput

if selectedItem and quantity > 0 then
    print("Item '" .. selectedItem.name .. "' x" .. quantity .. " has been delivered.")
else
    print("Invalid selection or quantity.")
end

import aiohttp
import asyncio
import re
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup

async def get_token_data(session, urls):
    tasks = [fetch(session, url) for url in urls]
    pages_content = await asyncio.gather(*tasks)

    result = {}
    for url, page_content in zip(urls, pages_content):
        chain = re.findall(r"(bscscan|etherscan|arbiscan).*(0x.{40})", url)
        if len(chain) != 1 or len(chain[0]) != 2:
            print('Strange chain', url)
            continue
        address = chain[0][1]
        chain = chain[0][0]

        soup = BeautifulSoup(page_content, 'html.parser')
        title_text = soup.title.string
        price, name, _ = [part.strip() for part in title_text.split("|")]
        name = name.split()[0].upper()
        price = float(price.replace('$', ''))

        if chain in result:
            result[chain][name] = (address, price)
        else:
            result[chain] = {name: (address, price)}

    return result

async def fetch(session, url):
    async with session.get(url) as response:
        return await response.text()

async def main():
    urls = ['http://example.com', 'http://example2.com'] 
    async with aiohttp.ClientSession() as session:
        result = await get_token_data(session, urls)
        print(result)

asyncio.run(main())

content:
#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#

import tkinter as tk
import pprint

# defino mi estructura de datos:
# lista = [
#       {"nombre": "Ana"},
#       {"nac": "Argentina"},
#       {"tel": "11-2525-2257"}
# ]
#

def guardar_datos():
    global lista
    
    # leo los datos del formulario
    nombre = caja_nombre.get()
    nac = caja_nac.get()
    tel = caja_tel.get()
    
    # creo el diccionario con los datos leídos
    persona = {"nombre":nombre, "nac":nac, "tel":tel}
    
    # agrego el diccionario de datos a la lista
    lista.append(persona)
    pprint.pprint(lista)
    
    # borro el formulario
    caja_nac.delete(0, tk.END)
    caja_nombre.delete(0, tk.END)
    caja_tel.delete(0, tk.END)
    
    
    

lista = []


ventana = tk.Tk()
ventana.config(width=300, height=280, bg="dark slate gray")
ventana.title("Formulario")
ventana.resizable(False,False) # evita redimensionar la ventana

# campo nombre

title: form con tkinter
content:
#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#

import tkinter as tk
import pprint

# defino mi estructura de datos:
# lista = [
#       {"nombre": "Ana"},
#       {"nac": "Argentina"},
#       {"tel": "11-2525-2257"}
# ]
#

def guardar_datos():
    global lista
    
    # leo los datos del formulario
    nombre = caja_nombre.get()
    nac = caja_nac.get()
    tel = caja_tel.get()
    
    # creo el diccionario con los datos leídos
    persona = {"nombre":nombre, "nac":nac, "tel":tel}
    
    # agrego el diccionario de datos a la lista
    lista.append(persona)
    pprint.pprint(lista)
    
    # borro el formulario
    caja_nac.delete(0, tk.END)
    caja_nombre.delete(0, tk.END)
    caja_tel.delete(0, tk.END)
    
    
    

lista = []


ventana = tk.Tk()
ventana.config(width=300, height=280)
ventana.title("Formulario")
ventana.resizable(False,False) # evita redimensionar la ventana

# campo nombre
etiqueta = tk.Label(text="Nombre")
etiqueta.place(x=10, y=10)
caja_nombre = tk.Entry()
caja_nombre.place(x=100, y=10, width=150, height=24)


# campo nacionalidad
etiqueta = tk.Label(text="Nacionalidad")
etiqueta.place(x=10, y=70)
caja_nac = tk.Entry()
caja_nac.place(x=100, y=70, width=150, height=24)


# campo telefono
etiqueta = tk.Label(text="Teléfono")
etiqueta.place(x=10, y=130)
caja_tel = tk.Entry()
caja_tel.place(x=100, y=130, width=150, height=24)


# boton
boton = tk.Button(text="Guardar", command=guardar_datos)
boton.place(x=120, y=200, width=80, height=35)


ventana.mainloop()
